<h2 id="marriage" class="coloured">Searching for a marriage</h2>

<p class="flush--bottom">With marriage searches, you must at least:</p>
<ul>
    <li>enter the <strong>Surname of the Groom</strong> or the <strong>surname of the Bride</strong> </li>
    <li>select a <strong>County</strong> from the drop down list</li>
</ul>
<p>More complex searches can be done using any of the other search options.</p>

